{"tid":1962094,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本】靜岡廢老東京連人帶菌返屋企","createTime":"2020-04-07T08:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T08:44:10.000Z","uid":207951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"410cc8b9626070a8d797a88ba2b8a7f112f80775","tid":1962094,"uid":207951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"Source: 產經新聞 <a href=\"https://t.co/k2luM3TwcS?amp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fk2luM3TwcS%3Famp%3D1&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=c2ae876e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/k2luM3TwcS?amp=1</a><br />\n<br />\n靜岡縣於本月７日新增兩宗武漢肺炎確診病例，總數增至21宗。其中一名為居住松崎町的70歲代男子，於三連假的3月22日在東京上野公園賞花，懷疑於該處感染。另一名患者為居住榛原郡的20歲代男子，在東京居留至3月下旬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5fWKBGN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fWKBGN.png&h=0861d738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n風頭火勢仲去東京睇櫻花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日本最活躍全部係班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}